headline: This 4%-Yielding Dividend Stock Continues to Provide a Safe Haven From Market Storms
summary: Tariffs could cause a severe economic downturn, depending on who you listen to.  Its resiliency during turbulent times and high-yielding dividend make it a safe haven during market storms.  "Obviously, we are going through turbulent times, with some voicing fears of an economic downturn," stated Richard Kinder, Kinder Morgan's co-founder and executive chairman, in the company's recent first-quarter earnings report.
